</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-25_ pf-text-1">In a survey conducted by Healthcare Learning Innovations, 78% of healthcare professionals affirmed that group discussions positively impact their understanding of clinical procedures and protocols.


































































