</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-58_ pf-text-1">Utilise diverse teaching modalities, such as case studies, role-plays, and problem-solving exercises, to enrich group discussions and cater to different learning styles.




































































